The Nairobi Expressway toll rates are subject to adjustment as per the Consumer Price Index and Exchange Rate.With the exception of foreigners, who will pay in dollars, the toll will be paid in local currency. The Nairobi Expressway is, in less than a year, quickly unfolding from a concept to a towering piece of infrastructure which will soon be floating along one of Kenya’s busiest road corridors.
The first of its kind in the country, it has attracted public attention for the nature of its construction and how it will operate as a toll road.



